I still have my earth staff from PoH. Would any of you suggest using that for making a beefier earth pet and reclaiming after the fight over using the stein of moggok or ruby steins (+10 to all resists)? I can get my disease resist up to around 60-65 while using the earth staff or 85-90 if I use the stein of moggok. <p>-Tweelis Twitchydigits<br>
